<section id="fieldselection">
<h1 id="par_idN10546"><link href="text/sdatabase/querywizard01.xhp">Query Wizard - Field Selection</link></h1>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10556" xml-lang="en-US">Specifies the table to create the query, and specifies which fields you wish to include in the query.</paragraph>
</section>
